title: 91. $600? Ft. Will Grimes & Eli Schmidt
itunes:title: 91. $600? Ft. Will Grimes & Eli Schmidt
description: How do you feel about other countries getting a stimulus check from our tax dollars while suffering Americans only receive $600? On today's podcast, Andy and the crew are joined by Will Grimes & Eli Schmidt from Day One Dollar Zero Podcast as they discuss the stimulus check, what it takes to be a man, and why small businesses are crucial to America's economy.
